reviewText: Instant flashbacks of my childhood... The tape arrived in perfect condition, as described. Would recommend to anyone who loves the muppets and is looking for a blast from the past!
My daughter watched this until she wore it out--this was to replace the old one.  It was shipped quickly and arrived in great condition.
We got the tape which plays good, our kids are happy.. even it was old one! Thank you & have a nice day!
Nice old sing along tape for the kids (and adults too).  Too bad I couldn't find a DVD in the internet.
Video arrived very timely and in good condition.  Have watched it several times already and am very pleased with my purchase.  I would buy from this seller again!
